WEBVTT

00:00.134 --> 00:02.835
♪♪

00:10.711 --> 00:13.779
All through history,
countries go to war.

00:13.781 --> 00:15.547
That's what we normally
study in here.

00:15.549 --> 00:18.884
But today,
we're going to talk
about peace and forgiveness

00:18.886 --> 00:20.953
And how we get there.

00:20.955 --> 00:23.455
Every once in a while,
I come up with a good idea.

00:23.457 --> 00:26.458
What could it possibly be
that I haven't already
thought of?

00:26.460 --> 00:28.394
Farkle, I forgive you.

00:28.396 --> 00:30.696
-What did I do?
-I forgive you too.

00:30.698 --> 00:34.299
-What did I do?
-You know what you do.

00:34.301 --> 00:37.136
I feel better
now that I've forgiven you.
How do you feel?

00:37.138 --> 00:39.805
I'm sorry for every time
I've hurt you!
What did I do?

00:39.807 --> 00:44.143
Ladies and gentlemen,
today we're going to begin
the forgiveness project.

00:44.145 --> 00:46.879
Our history isn't just
about what we've done.

00:46.881 --> 00:49.715
How we grow
comes from the repair
of what we've done

00:49.717 --> 00:52.484
And how we forgive
what was done to us.

00:52.486 --> 00:54.820
Hmm. We're in.
What do we do?

00:54.822 --> 00:56.989
Everyone take out
a piece of paper.

00:56.991 --> 00:59.992
So this isn't your laptop
or your cell phone.

00:59.994 --> 01:03.028
You've got
unlimited characters here.

01:03.030 --> 01:04.730
As many words as you want.

01:04.732 --> 01:07.399
The impact will last longer
than six seconds.

01:07.401 --> 01:10.169
And I guarantee you,
it's never going to disappear.

01:10.171 --> 01:14.339
So pick up a pen.
Express feelings.

01:14.341 --> 01:17.042
This is one of
the most important things
you're ever going to do.

01:17.044 --> 01:19.011
You're about
to forgive someone.

01:19.013 --> 01:20.779
What's this got to do
with history, matthews?

01:20.781 --> 01:22.114
It gives you a chance
to change it.

01:22.116 --> 01:24.783
Like when I forgave auggie
for biting the face

01:24.785 --> 01:27.119
Off my beary-the-bear bear.

01:27.121 --> 01:29.354
That wasn't forgiveness,
honey.

01:29.356 --> 01:32.291
-Why not?
-Because you haven't
gotten over it.

01:32.293 --> 01:36.495
This is the first thing
I see every day.

01:37.765 --> 01:40.432
So is there anyone
in your life

01:40.434 --> 01:44.269
That you want to forgive?
Change your history. Go.

01:46.807 --> 01:49.942
"dear auggie
the murderer..."

01:51.445 --> 01:55.047
Maya, no one in your life
you want to forgive?

01:55.049 --> 01:57.049
No.

01:57.051 --> 02:00.018
Don't you think now
would be a good time?

02:01.589 --> 02:04.056
You and your mom
are in a good place.

02:04.058 --> 02:05.891
You're strong, maya.

02:05.893 --> 02:08.627
Don't you want to forgive him
one day? Why not now?

02:10.564 --> 02:12.798
Hmm.

02:13.934 --> 02:16.635
-(maya laughs)
-(chuckling)

02:21.108 --> 02:22.774
Ahem.

02:22.776 --> 02:25.177
"riley,

02:25.179 --> 02:26.812
"butt out.

02:28.449 --> 02:31.216
"I am serious.
Butt your butt out."

02:32.520 --> 02:34.319
I forgive you.

02:37.258 --> 02:39.658
<i>(theme music playing)</i>

02:41.162 --> 02:43.495
<i>♪ I've been waiting ♪</i>

02:43.497 --> 02:45.364
<i>♪ for a day like this to come ♪</i>

02:45.366 --> 02:47.266
<i>♪ struck like lightning ♪</i>

02:47.268 --> 02:49.501
<i>♪ my heart's beating</i>
<i>like a drum ♪</i>

02:49.503 --> 02:52.304
<i>♪ on the edge of something ♪</i>

02:52.306 --> 02:53.639
<i>♪ wonderful ♪</i>

02:53.641 --> 02:56.475
<i>♪ face to face</i>
<i>with changes ♪</i>

02:56.477 --> 02:58.010
<i>♪ what's it all about? ♪</i>

02:58.012 --> 02:59.811
<i>♪ life is crazy ♪</i>

02:59.813 --> 03:01.847
<i>♪ but I know</i>
<i>I can work it out ♪</i>

03:01.849 --> 03:06.118
<i>♪ 'cause I got you</i>
<i>to live it with me ♪</i>

03:06.120 --> 03:10.189
<i>♪ I feel all right,</i>
<i>I'm gonna take on the world ♪</i>

03:10.191 --> 03:13.292
<i>♪ light up the stars,</i>
<i>I've got some pages to turn ♪</i>

03:13.294 --> 03:15.894
<i>♪ I'm singing, "oh oh oh ♪</i>

03:15.896 --> 03:18.530
<i>♪ "oh oh oh oh" ♪</i>

03:18.532 --> 03:21.633
<i>♪ take on the world,</i>
